casebody.data:
Argued and submitted September 15, appeal dismissed November 24, 2010, petition for review denied April 7, 2011 (350 Or 230) CITY OF EUGENE, Plaintiff-Respondent, v. SHANNON J. SMYTH, aka Shannon Jensen Smyth, Defendant-Appellant.

Lane County Circuit Court

250828825; A141645 245 P3d 146 John Halpern, Jr., argued the cause and filed the brief for appellant. Joña J. Maukonen argued the cause for respondent. With her on the brief were C. Robert Steringer and Harrang Long Gary Rudnick P.C. Before Haselton, Presiding Judge, and Armstrong, Judge, and Duncan, Judge. PER CURIAM

Appeal dismissed. City of Eugene v. Smyth (A141624), 239 Or App 175, 243 P3d 854 (2010).
